# Save the Whale 

## Step 1 - Adding a background 

Go to the Scene folder and add "set background color to" tile
 inside the "on start" tile and 
set up the color light blue by clicking on it 

```blocks
scene.setBackgroundColor(9)
```

## Step 2 Adding the whale
Go to "Sprites" folder and select "set mySprite to sprite of kind Player"
and add it to under "set background",
then click on the sprite and select the Whale_right under the assets
```blocks
let mySprite = sprites.create(img`
```
